The paper discusses deep learning methods for answering non-factoid questions, specifically in the context of love advice. This suggests that the paper falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP) and computational linguistics (CL), which is represented by cs.CL. The paper also involves the use of neural networks and machine learning algorithms, which are common in the sub-categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with information retrieval (IR) and the optimization of sentence combinations, which are relevant to the sub-category of information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE), respectively.
